Interactive application, made for young kids or adults learning the English language
When a picture of an animal is clicked audio is played, saying the name of the animal and spelling the animal.

When next page button is clicked, a page appears with list of animals, where clicking on an animal - large text will appear, 
you can read small sentences, and the application will read it for you for you to practice reading correctly,
this helps kids and adults learn reading, listening and perfect their English language.
